+	// in THIS archive, and that material is itself nested in encrypted zones (domino):
+	//   - systemwide DE ("DK")  <- /data/unencrypted/key      (NONE policy, readable immediately)
+	//   - user-0 DE   ("DE0")   <- /data/misc/.../de/0         (DK-encrypted: needs DK in keyring)
+	//   - user-0 CE   ("CE0")   <- /data/system/locksettings.db + /data/system_de/0/spblob/*
+	//                              + /data/misc/keystore + /data/misc/.../ce/0 (DE0-encrypted)
+	// So we pull the key material out in dependency order, running de_keyinstall after each stage
